title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 5 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 5 2022
description:
Fox News's Gianno Caldwell joins Clay and Buck to discuss his younger brother Christian's murder in Chicago and the soft-on-crime policies destroying families and our cities. Growing calls from Democrats saying Biden shouldn't run in 2024. Democrats plan on ramming a tax increase bill for the midterm elections. $300,000 raised for Burger King employee, who never missed work in 27 years and got mediocre gift.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
